b'Congratulations to the following Brown-Forman brands for bringing home many awards at this year\xe2\x80\x99s @sfwspiritscomp!

@oldforester: Two Double-Golds (Straight Bourbon Category) for 1920 Prohibition Style Kentucky Straight Bourbon and 100 Proof Kentucky Straight Bourbon.

@jackdaniels_us: Two Double-Golds (TN Whiskey Category) for Single Barrel Select and Single Barrel Barrel Proof.

@Glendronach: Multiple Best in Class Awards for The GlenDronach including GlenDronach 15 being named Best Whisky in the World.

@Benriach: Gold and Double Gold Awards.

@glenglassaugh: Full core range wins top accolades as the distillery begins to come of age.

@slanewhiskey: Gold (Blended Irish Whiskey Category) for Blended Triple Cask Irish Whiskey.

@WoodfordReserve: Gold (Rye Whiskey Category) for Woodford Reserve Rye.

@earlytimeswhisky: Two Double-Golds for Early Times Kentucky Whisky (Other Whisky Category) Early Times Bottled-In-Bond (Straight Bourbon Category).
